Edmonton International Results
March 15-16, 2008

      Judo Saskatchewan returns with over 35 medals from the Edmonton International Judo Championships at the West Edmonton Mall (Ice Palace) on March 15th & 16th, 2008. Judo Saskatchewan has attended this International tournament with a team of four referees and has entrants in sixty six comptetitions. On the first day, in forty competitions, Saskatchewan returned 21 medals.

      The official results http://www.edmontonjudo.com/files/Edmonton_International/2008/Results/Tabmed.htm
